            <p class="eyebrow">Service overview</p>
            <h2>What hydro jetting actually solves</h2>
            <p>Cabling cuts a hole through a clog. Hydro jetting cleans the entire inside of the pipe so the line behaves like new. For grease lines, cast iron with scale, and roots in a clay sewer, jetting is the difference between a temporary fix and a real cleaning.</p><p>Honest Drain matches nozzle and pressure to the line: a chain or chisel nozzle for scale, a flushing nozzle for grease, and a root-cutting nozzle for clay sewers. After the line is clean, a camera review confirms the job and documents the pipe condition.</p>
            <p class="link-row"><a class="text-link" href="../../contact.html">Book a service visit</a></p>
